---
layout: layouts/base.njk
title: Nearly 1,000 Free Online Games - ArcadeNest
description: Play nearly 1,000 free online games on ArcadeNest with zero downloads, no sign-ups, and instant browser access to racing, simulator, shooting, survival, puzzle, and arcade games.
---
{% import "components/game-card.njk" as cards %}
{% import "components/sidebar-nav.njk" as sidebar %}
{% set currentLocale = locale | default(site.locale) | default("en-US") %}
{% set rankedGames = games.games | rankGamesForLocale(currentLocale) %}
{% set surpriseGame = rankedGames[0] %}
<div class="layout-shell layout-shell--catalog">
  {{ sidebar.catalogSidebar(games.sidebarTags, page.url, "") }}

  <div class="catalog-content">
    <section class="catalog-hero">
      <h1>Nearly 1,000 Games. Zero Downloads. Endless Fun.</h1>
      <p>No installs, no sign-ups, no waiting. Just open your browser and start playing racing, shooting, survival, puzzles, and more, all free and ready in seconds.</p>
      <div class="catalog-hero__actions" aria-label="Homepage actions">
        <a class="button button--primary" data-surprise-link href="/games/{{ surpriseGame.slug }}/">Surprise Me</a>
        <a class="button button--secondary" href="#featured-games">Browse All Games</a>
      </div>
      <div class="trust-bar" aria-label="ArcadeNest catalog facts">
        <span>Nearly 1,000 Games</span>
        <span>Instant Browser Play</span>
        <span>10+ Categories</span>
        <span>Always Free</span>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="catalog-section" id="featured-games" aria-labelledby="featured-games-title">
      <div class="section__heading">
        <h2 id="featured-games-title">What Are You In the Mood For?</h2>
        <p>From high-speed drifts to last-player-standing survival, pick a vibe and find a game that starts fast.</p>
      </div>
      <nav class="mood-tags" aria-label="Popular game moods">
        <a href="/t/racing/">Racing &amp; Drift</a>
        <a href="/t/shooting/">Shooting &amp; Sniper</a>
        <a href="/t/puzzle/">Puzzle &amp; Chill</a>
        <a href="/t/survival/">Survival</a>
        <a href="/t/sports/">Sports</a>
        <a href="/t/action/">Action</a>
        <a href="/t/arcade/">Arcade Classics</a>
        <a href="/new-games/">New Arrivals</a>
      </nav>
      <p class="scroll-hook">Scroll down. Your next favorite game is probably 3 rows away.</p>
      <div class="dense-game-grid dense-game-grid--home">
        {% for game in rankedGames %}
          {{ cards.denseCard(game) }}
        {% endfor %}
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="catalog-section homepage-seo" aria-labelledby="arcadenest-guide-title">
      <div class="section__heading">
        <h2 id="arcadenest-guide-title">Find Your Next Browser Game</h2>
        <p>ArcadeNest is built for players who want quick sessions, clear categories, and free online games that open directly in the browser.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="homepage-seo__grid">
        <article class="homepage-seo__card">
          <h3>Racing, Drift, and Car Games</h3>
          <p>Start with racing games, drift games, and car games when you want speed, tight turns, highway traffic, stunt tracks, or vehicle challenges that feel familiar to US and European arcade players.</p>
        </article>
        <article class="homepage-seo__card">
          <h3>Simulator, Survival, and Sniper Games</h3>
          <p>ArcadeNest also highlights simulator games, survival games, and sniper games for players who prefer objectives, precision, upgrades, waves, and longer browser game sessions.</p>
        </article>
        <article class="homepage-seo__card">
          <h3>Clicker, Puzzle, and Arcade Games</h3>
          <p>For relaxed play, choose clicker games, puzzle games, sports games, io games, or classic arcade games from ArcadeNest and jump into a free online game in seconds.</p>
        </article>
      </div>
    </section>
  </div>
</div>

<script type="application/ld+json">{"@context":"https://schema.org","@type":"WebSite","name":"{{ site.name }}","url":"{{ site.domain }}/","potentialAction":{"@type":"SearchAction","target":"{{ site.domain }}/?q={search_term_string}","query-input":"required name=search_term_string"}}</script>
